               <note>This incipit is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="EMML3872"/>.</note>
                 <ab>
                     ወሀሎ፡ አሐዱ፡ ብእሲ፡ ሠራቂ፡ ዘይሴሰይ፡ በሠሪቅ፡ ወባሕቱ፡ ይሁብ፡ ሰላማ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS6437Macomber"/>
                     ብዙኃ፡ ጊዜያት፡ በልብ፡ ንጹሕ፡ <choice>
                     <corr resp="PRS6437Macomber">ወበትሕትና፡</corr>
                     <sic>ወትሕትና፡</sic></choice> ወበየውሃት፣
                     ወሶበ፡ ኮነ፡ ይዜክር፡ ስማ፡ ይትሀወክ፡ እስመ፡ ፍቅራ፡ ውስተ፡ ልቡ።
                 </ab>
                 <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                    <note>This incipit is perhaps taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="EMML3275"/>, Macomber sais EMML327, which is incorrect.</note>
